==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Water measure
<hw>Wa"ter meas"ure</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A measure formerly used for
articles brought by water, as coals, oysters, etc. The water-measure
bushel was three gallons larger than the Winchester bushel.</def>
<rj><au>Cowell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Water measurer</ent>⟦br⟧
